<p class="ayah 32-10" id="10" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَءِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Is (it) when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضَلَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we are lost</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَءِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will we</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَفِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">certainly be in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلْقٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a creation</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَدِيدِۭ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">new?`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِلِقَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in (the) meeting</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl