<p class="ayah 32-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَوَفَّـٰكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Will take your soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّلَكُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Angel</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the death</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the one who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وُكِّلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has been put in charge</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُرْجَعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be returned.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>11<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
