<span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنْعَـٰمُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their cattle</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنفُسُهُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they themselves?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُبْصِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they see?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>27<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 32-28" id="28" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَقُولُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَتَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`When (will be)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْفَتْحُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">decision,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you are</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَـٰدِقِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">truthful?`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>28<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 32-29" id="29" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`(On the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْفَتْحِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Decision,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنفَعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will benefit</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِيمَـٰنُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their belief</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُنظَرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will be granted respite.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>29<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 32-30" id="30" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَعْرِضْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So turn away</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱنتَظِرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and wait.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّنتَظِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) waiting.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>30<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
